# Follow the steps from the section *Step 2: Create the client* of the developer document [OAuth|https://developer.atlassian.com/server/jira/platform/oauth/] to obtain a test OAuth client. 
(!) *Use the following values when modifying the file {{PropertiesClient.java}} (changing {{JIRA_HOME}} is fine), otherwise there will be a mismatch between public and private keys:*
